name: La Jugada - Prieto - Ancho
additionalNotes: La Jugada Habano is gorgeously constructed with the same Nicaraguan binder and long-leaf fillers as Prieto, but the difference is on the outside. A gorgeous, rich and oily Ecuadorian Habano tops off this little stunner. A cornucopia of complex flavors awaits you here, with notes of spice, nuts, and cream making their debuts during the creamy, oh-so-smooth experience.Â
